            "content": "<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\">\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p class=\"editor-paragraph\"></p>\r\n<p>This a test recurring meeting for this specific team channel.</p>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"me-email-text\" lang=\"en-GB\" style=\"max-width:1024px; color:#242424; font-family:'Segoe UI','Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\">\r\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"margin-bottom:24px; overflow:hidden; white-space:nowrap\">\r\n________________________________________________________________________________</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:12px\"><span class=\"me-email-text\" style=\"font-size:20px; color:#242424; font-weight:600\">Microsoft Teams meeting</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:6px\"><span class=\"me-email-text\" style=\"font-size:20px; color:#242424; font-weight:600\">Join:\r\n</span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/meet/274202807263092?p=euDlm8IjKMen2lo7BV\" id=\"meet_invite_block.action.join_link\" title=\"Meeting join\" aria-label=\"Meeting join\" class=\"me-email-link\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-decoration:underline; color:#5B5FC7\">https://teams.microsoft.com/meet/274202807263092?p=euDlm8IjKMen2lo7BV</a>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:6px\"><span class=\"me-email-text-secondary\" style=\"font-size:14px; color:#616161\">Meeting ID:\r\n</span><span class=\"me-email-text\" style=\"font-size:14px; color:#242424\">274 202 807 263 092</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:32px\"><span class=\"me-email-text-secondary\" style=\"font-size:14px; color:#616161\">Passcode:\r\n</span><span class=\"me-email-text\" style=\"font-size:14px; color:#242424\">NN6e5CW3</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:12px; max-width:1024px\">\r\n<hr style=\"border:0; background:#616161; height:1px\">\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:24px\"><a href=\"https://aka.ms/JoinTeamsMeeting?omkt=en-GB\" id=\"meet_invite_block.action.help\" class=\"me-email-link\" style=\"font-size:14px; text-decoration:underline; color:#5B5FC7\">Need help?</a>\r\n<span style=\"color:#616161\">|</span> <a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meetup-join/19%3aSYrI53FHoUqr9lgEI_8_1LJAIkh4oDLwodsWvXs-GgU1%40thread.tacv2/1777986122199?context=%7b%22Tid%22%3a%2263982aff-fb6c-4c22-973b-70e4acfb63e6%22%2c%22Oid%22%3a%22420a2572-f2f7-4c85-80dc-ea6478de394b%22%7d\" id=\"meet_invite_block.action.join_link_compatibility\" class=\"me-email-link\" style=\"font-size:14px; text-decoration:underline; color:#5B5FC7\">\r\nSystem reference</a> </div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:6px\"><span class=\"me-email-headline\" style=\"font-size:16px; color:#242424; font-weight:600\">Join on a video conferencing device</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:6px\"><span class=\"me-email-text\" style=\"font-size:14px; color:#616161\">Tenant key:\r\n</span><span class=\"me-email-text\" style=\"font-size:14px; color:#242424\">gsk@m.webex.com</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:6px\"><span class=\"me-email-text-secondary\" style=\"font-size:14px; color:#616161\">Video ID:\r\n</span><span class=\"me-email-text\" style=\"font-size:14px; color:#242424\">116 873 325 73</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:24px\"><a href=\"https://www.webex.com/msteams?confid=11687332573&amp;tenantkey=gsk&amp;domain=m.webex.com\" id=\"meet_invite_block.action.join_vtc_info\" class=\"me-email-link\" style=\"font-size:14px; text-decoration:underline; color:#5B5FC7\">More\r\n info</a> </div>\r\n<div><span class=\"me-email-text-secondary\" style=\"font-size:14px; color:#616161\">For organisers:\r\n</span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/meetingOptions/?organizerId=420a2572-f2f7-4c85-80dc-ea6478de394b&amp;tenantId=63982aff-fb6c-4c22-973b-70e4acfb63e6&amp;threadId=19_SYrI53FHoUqr9lgEI_8_1LJAIkh4oDLwodsWvXs-GgU1@thread.tacv2&amp;messageId=1777986122199&amp;language=en-GB\" id=\"meet_invite_block.action.organizer_meet_options\" class=\"me-email-link\" style=\"font-size:14px; text-decoration:underline; color:#5B5FC7\">Meeting\r\n options</a> </div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-top:24px; margin-bottom:6px\">\r\n<div class=\"me-email-text-secondary\" style=\"color:#616161; font-size:14px\">Be sure to use a recommended audio device and have a strong internet connection before joining. You can join clientless via Edge or Chrome browser. Don't forget to tell us about the\r\n quality of your meeting, if asked via the Teams Meeting survey. </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:24px\"><a href=\"https://servicenow.gsk.com/home?id=kb_article&amp;table=kb_knowledge&amp;sys_kb_id=86c5dd1f1b65d150436f848ae54bcb74\" id=\"meet_invite_block.action.org_help\" class=\"me-email-link\" style=\"font-size:14px; text-decoration:underline; color:#5B5FC7\">Org\r\n help</a> </div>\r\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"margin-bottom:24px; overflow:hidden; white-space:nowrap\">\r\n________________________________________________________________________________</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n-----------------<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAfter processing the next meeting event for \\nVitor Recurring Weekly Sync Event \\nhappening on \\n2026-05-15 \\n\\nthis is my suggested list of mandatory and optional attendees:\\n\\nMandatory attendees: \\n- vitor.x.antonio@gsk.com \\n- dilawar.x.mansoori@gsk.com\r\n \\n\\nThese mandatory attendees have a required DIA Task associated with the meeting event or have submitted a DIA for the meeting event.\\n\\nOptional attendees: \\n- sukant.x.sondhi@gsk.com \\n- ana.x.ocarizsanchez@gsk.com \\n\\nThese optional attendees have no\r\n required DIA Tasks assigned to them or haven't submitted any optional DIAs.\r\n<p></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n"
